Description: wl-android Wayland backend plugin (wlroots)
 wl-android is a Wayland backend plugin that forwards wlroots
 framebuffer output to Android devices via SCM_RIGHTS.
 .
 This package provides libland_wlroots.so for Droidspaces containers.

Package: landd
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, land (= ${binary:Version})
Description: wl-android container daemon
 System daemon for wl-android that manages the socket forwarding
 between the wlroots backend and the Android application.
